          "username": "Shobana-vz"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-14 09:36:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAnd I have removed the code part related to maintaining the state of Vms in database as per the mail the chain. will attach the mail chain in JIRA",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
